## My process

### Built with

- Semantic HTML5 markup
- CSS custom properties
- Flexbox
- Mobile-first workflow
- Git command

### What I learned

I learn to use the git command and i force me to use "git add -p" and "git commit -m" a lot of time. I work on a different branch just for merge my job at the finish. I use css variable and layer. It's really fun.

```css
@layer reset, style, typo;
@import 'reset.css';
@import 'typo.css';

```
```css
:root{
    --bg-color: #f4d04e;
    --card-color: #ffffff;
    --color1: #111111;  
    --spacing1: 24px;
    --spacing2: 12px;
    --spacing3: 8px;
    --spacing4: 4px;
}
```

### Continued development
I need to perform in css comprehension

